{
  "video_id": "Y0UB6g8Rsyw",
  "title": "Capitalism isn't an ideology -- it's an operating system | Bhu Srinivasan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12881.0,
      "end_time": 14470.0,
      "text": "So, what is capitalism?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14710.0,
      "end_time": 17261.0,
      "text": "Capitalism, fundamentally, is a series of marketplaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17285.0,
      "end_time": 19199.0,
      "text": "You can have a marketplace for lemonade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19223.0,
      "end_time": 20508.0,
      "text": "a marketplace for lemons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20532.0,
      "end_time": 22911.0,
      "text": "a marketplace for trucks that transport lemons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22935.0,
      "end_time": 25490.0,
      "text": "a marketplace that fuels those trucks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25514.0,
      "end_time": 28902.0,
      "text": "marketplaces that sell wood to build lemonade stands."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28926.0,
      "end_time": 31371.0,
      "text": "However, capitalism of course, as we know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31395.0,
      "end_time": 33831.0,
      "text": "is this either celebrated term"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33855.0,
      "end_time": 35600.0,
      "text": "or condemned term."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35300.0,
      "end_time": 37270.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s either revered or it&#39;s reviled."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37649.0,
      "end_time": 41400.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m here to argue that this is because capitalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41280.0,
      "end_time": 44229.0,
      "text": "in the modern iteration, is largely misunderstood."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44982.0,
      "end_time": 46141.0,
      "text": "In my view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46165.0,
      "end_time": 48974.0,
      "text": "capitalism should not be thought of as an ideology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48998.0,
      "end_time": 52275.0,
      "text": "but instead should be thought of as an operating system."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52849.0,
      "end_time": 54117.0,
      "text": "Think of your iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54762.0,
      "end_time": 58659.0,
      "text": "Your iPhone merges hardware with software."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58683.0,
      "end_time": 60470.0,
      "text": "Apps and hardware."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60710.0,
      "end_time": 63808.0,
      "text": "Now think about all the hardware as the physical reality all around you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63832.0,
      "end_time": 66600.0,
      "text": "and think of the apps as entrepreneurial activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66624.0,
      "end_time": 67774.0,
      "text": "creative energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68188.0,
      "end_time": 70863.0,
      "text": "And in-between, you have an operating system."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71307.0,
      "end_time": 73537.0,
      "text": "As you have advances in hardware,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73561.0,
      "end_time": 75537.0,
      "text": "you have advances in software."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75561.0,
      "end_time": 77569.0,
      "text": "And the operating system needs to keep up."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77593.0,
      "end_time": 80529.0,
      "text": "It needs to be patched, it needs to be updated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80553.0,
      "end_time": 82458.0,
      "text": "new releases have to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82482.0,
      "end_time": 85441.0,
      "text": "And all of these things have to happen symbiotically."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85465.0,
      "end_time": 88767.0,
      "text": "The operating system needs to keep getting more and more advanced"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88791.0,
      "end_time": 90591.0,
      "text": "to keep up with innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91728.0,
      "end_time": 94109.0,
      "text": "And this is why, fundamentally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94133.0,
      "end_time": 96339.0,
      "text": "when you think about it as an operating system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96363.0,
      "end_time": 98512.0,
      "text": "it devolves the language of ideology"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98536.0,
      "end_time": 102212.0,
      "text": "away from what traditional defenders of capitalism think."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102236.0,
      "end_time": 104103.0,
      "text": "But even if you go to the constitution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104127.0,
      "end_time": 107374.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll notice, before the founders even got to the First Amendment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107398.0,
      "end_time": 110673.0,
      "text": "with free speech, free religion, free press,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110697.0,
      "end_time": 113710.0,
      "text": "they thought about patents and copyright."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113950.0,
      "end_time": 117267.0,
      "text": "They talked about the government&#39;s role in promoting arts and sciences."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117645.0,
      "end_time": 122580.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the reason why I could not start a search engine tomorrow called Goggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122820.0,
      "end_time": 123440.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123464.0,
      "end_time": 125140.0,
      "text": "Google doesn&#39;t own Gs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125164.0,
      "end_time": 127943.0,
      "text": "but I couldn&#39;t do it because there could be some confusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127967.0,
      "end_time": 130582.0,
      "text": "So even property rights have ambiguity built into them."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 131173.0,
      "end_time": 132482.0,
      "text": "And on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 132506.0,
      "end_time": 136862.0,
      "text": "And by 1900, you have other types of property that come into being."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136886.0,
      "end_time": 140743.0,
      "text": "For instance, imagine that in 1900, you owned 100 acres of land"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140767.0,
      "end_time": 142186.0,
      "text": "someplace in the Midwest."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142709.0,
      "end_time": 144804.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very easy to see where your fence ends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144828.0,
      "end_time": 146462.0,
      "text": "your neighbor&#39;s property begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 146486.0,
      "end_time": 147649.0,
      "text": "Now let me ask you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 147673.0,
      "end_time": 150470.0,
      "text": "where in the sky does your property end?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 150710.0,
      "end_time": 151752.0,
      "text": "Does it end at 1,000 feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 151776.0,
      "end_time": 154117.0,
      "text": "5,000 feet, 10,000 feet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 154141.0,
      "end_time": 155323.0,
      "text": "It makes no difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 155348.0,
      "end_time": 158363.0,
      "text": "because other than the novelty of a few hot-air balloons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 158387.0,
      "end_time": 159537.0,
      "text": "man couldn&#39;t fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 160530.0,
      "end_time": 161798.0,
      "text": "But within three years, he could."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 161822.0,
      "end_time": 164752.0,
      "text": "Now all of a sudden, it was very much relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 164776.0,
      "end_time": 167450.0,
      "text": "whether your land ends at 1,000 feet in the sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167474.0,
      "end_time": 169243.0,
      "text": "5,000 feet, 10,000 feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169665.0,
      "end_time": 172283.0,
      "text": "And you have to have someone arbitrate that."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 173116.0,
      "end_time": 175770.0,
      "text": "And indeed, that&#39;s exactly what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 175101.0,
      "end_time": 176614.0,
      "text": "And five or ten years from now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 176638.0,
      "end_time": 180226.0,
      "text": "when Amazon wants to deliver a package over your house to your neighbor"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 180250.0,
      "end_time": 181894.0,
      "text": "from that UPS truck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 181918.0,
      "end_time": 185180.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to have to decide: Does you property end at five feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185204.0,
      "end_time": 187912.0,
      "text": "10 feet, 50 feet, 100 feet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 187936.0,
      "end_time": 189111.0,
      "text": "Where does it end?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 189135.0,
      "end_time": 190858.0,
      "text": "And there is no ideology"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 190882.0,
      "end_time": 193447.0,
      "text": "that will tell you where your property ends."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194132.0,
      "end_time": 195632.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an operating system."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 196300.0,
      "end_time": 197180.0,
      "text": "And similarly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 197205.0,
      "end_time": 199283.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to see this with automobiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 199386.0,
      "end_time": 202108.0,
      "text": "A few years after the Wright brothers figured out flight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 202132.0,
      "end_time": 204304.0,
      "text": "human beings started using more and more cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 204328.0,
      "end_time": 205479.0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 205503.0,
      "end_time": 207789.0,
      "text": "the regulatory system -- the operating system --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207813.0,
      "end_time": 212387.0,
      "text": "had to be patched to all of a sudden address the safety of consumers."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 212411.0,
      "end_time": 215538.0,
      "text": "That the consumers of vehicles were presenting danger to horses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 215562.0,
      "end_time": 218495.0,
      "text": "other pedestrians, trolleys, what have you."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 218957.0,
      "end_time": 220108.0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 220132.0,
      "end_time": 223966.0,
      "text": "the drivers of these automobiles had to have driver&#39;s licenses, eye exams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 223990.0,
      "end_time": 226696.0,
      "text": "registered motor vehicles, speed limits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 226720.0,
      "end_time": 227934.0,
      "text": "rules of the road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 227958.0,
      "end_time": 232950.0,
      "text": "so that horses, pedestrians, could coexist with cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 232974.0,
      "end_time": 235174.0,
      "text": "It had to be backwards compatible."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 235199.0,
      "end_time": 239697.0,
      "text": "So a new invention had to basically fit advances from the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 240355.0,
      "end_time": 242179.0,
      "text": "Similarly, five or ten years from now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 242204.0,
      "end_time": 244995.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to see the same thing with self-driving cars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 245190.0,
      "end_time": 247149.0,
      "text": "coexisting with human-driven cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 247173.0,
      "end_time": 249497.0,
      "text": "The reason why this is important, is in 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 249521.0,
      "end_time": 252970.0,
      "text": "another thing is going to happen beyond drones and self-driving cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 252994.0,
      "end_time": 256161.0,
      "text": "but you&#39;re going to see the most valuable economy in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 256185.0,
      "end_time": 257882.0,
      "text": "the largest economy in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 257906.0,
      "end_time": 260174.0,
      "text": "is going to be a country run by communists."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 260558.0,
      "end_time": 263433.0,
      "text": "The Chinese seem to be very good at capitalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 264469.0,
      "end_time": 267945.0,
      "text": "And this is going to have fundamental problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 267970.0,
      "end_time": 271548.0,
      "text": "and present an identity crisis for the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 271572.0,
      "end_time": 273237.0,
      "text": "Because for a long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 273261.0,
      "end_time": 279118.0,
      "text": "free markets coincided with liberties such as free speech, free press,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279204.0,
      "end_time": 280506.0,
      "text": "free religion."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 280530.0,
      "end_time": 283996.0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, this equation is going to be decoupled."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 284644.0,
      "end_time": 286400.0,
      "text": "And when it gets decoupled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 286280.0,
      "end_time": 289696.0,
      "text": "we might find that democracy, the multitude of voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 289720.0,
      "end_time": 292156.0,
      "text": "actually impedes capitalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 292180.0,
      "end_time": 296186.0,
      "text": "because a state that does not have any pretense of limited government"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 296210.0,
      "end_time": 299751.0,
      "text": "can very quickly mandate a regulatory framework for drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 299776.0,
      "end_time": 302219.0,
      "text": "for electric cars, for self-driving cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 302243.0,
      "end_time": 304380.0,
      "text": "for any new innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 304620.0,
      "end_time": 307789.0,
      "text": "where they feel that they can leapfrog Western societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 308792.0,
      "end_time": 312671.0,
      "text": "And this is a very unique thing in the American experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 313236.0,
      "end_time": 317133.0,
      "text": "And this is why it&#39;s very important to think of American capitalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 317157.0,
      "end_time": 320306.0,
      "text": "as an operating system and not as an ideology."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 320331.0,
      "end_time": 322529.0,
      "text": "Because when you think about it as an ideology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 322553.0,
      "end_time": 327666.0,
      "text": "you can have good politics make for very, very bad policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 328371.0,
      "end_time": 331799.0,
      "text": "That market outcomes and democratic voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 331823.0,
      "end_time": 333474.0,
      "text": "and battles for votes"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 333498.0,
      "end_time": 335942.0,
      "text": "can end up stifling progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 337600.0,
      "end_time": 338982.0,
      "text": "So over the next few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 339600.0,
      "end_time": 341791.0,
      "text": "as this political cycle plays out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 341815.0,
      "end_time": 345451.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to see American democracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 345475.0,
      "end_time": 350973.0,
      "text": "rise to meet the challenges that capitalism poses and modernity poses."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 350997.0,
      "end_time": 354394.0,
      "text": "And I ask policymakers to think about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 355573.0,
      "end_time": 359780.0,
      "text": "decoupling ideology from economics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 359103.0,
      "end_time": 363440.0,
      "text": "and think about how good policy can ultimately become good politics."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 363793.0,
      "end_time": 364976.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 365000.0,
      "end_time": 369407.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}